                    <h2>Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) Software</h2>
                    <p>Our ERP software is a central hub for managing various aspects of a small business, including
                        finances, inventory, human resources, and more.</p>
                    <p>Features include financial management, procurement, inventory control, HR management, and
                        reporting tools.</p>
                    <p>It provides real-time insights, streamlines business processes, and ensures efficient resource
                        allocation.</p>
